99174c0944184941491068e16b3c77a0405","tid":537801,"uid":142358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T05:41:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">食屎狗</span>"},{"pid":"3269a1e689c6f0b2e67f22d4de6894724f97d826","tid":537801,"uid":123308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T05:49:37.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"9bff30cd6b51e4d5b832e3441bbf10c7d24612a3","tid":537801,"uid":160237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T05:50:58.000Z","msg":"因為呢個世界有隻狗種叫食屎狗"},{"pid":"946437caef4cf9c6a3bda59c5dcb940d351efe23","tid":537801,"uid":94009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T06:43:32.000Z","msg":"衲dee的驚身世秘密<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcd8dc56cc2c0d8ffd0e87fd7325c333b2fd0db2","tid":537801,"uid":517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T06:45:19.000Z","msg":"貓&gt;狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"513f51a516fa1e6d9b493b863912365a8e444d41","tid":537801,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T12:48:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbc3237146085d760e1a6eab10cd4c8770d304ac","tid":537801,"uid":142405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T13:55:04.000Z","msg":"八婆 八婆 食屎狗～！"},{"pid":"6790490097f2f3a73af9f3469170b2c6218a2533","tid":537801,"uid":126100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T14:02:27.000Z","msg":"好掛住馬車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff17334f34b9fbd50ac5e1c7feca50fe379b6024","tid":537801,"uid":15823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T14:24:57.000Z","msg":"為何狗會吃糞便?<br />\n為何人會看CCTVB?"},{"pid":"1725fc6b598798d41b080bf4bbc4384c0ce44cf3","tid":537801,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T00:38:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95eab410b5d26f69dd892e3852d4767119907776","tid":537801,"uid":8000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T00:43:25.000Z","msg":"睇到tvb以為nineup報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cce2a662611e01bf31f863aed3adeced79db57d8","tid":537801,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T00:43:48.000Z","msg":"好文共賞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1790eece386c67c04b1b141f3d2afe6b145cfa70","tid":537801,"uid":33597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T00:44:35.000Z","msg":"狗改不了吃屎"},{"pid":"b4713e1bea27448046f7b4c9b03b093139cc2a41","tid":537801,"uid":53189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T00:46:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>排泄物關注組織：上樓梯有助狗隻排便<br />\n<br />\n香港養狗的人士愈來愈多，但可曾有人關心過狗隻的排便習慣？近日有研究指出狗隻的排便習慣與上樓梯有直接關係，經常上樓梯的狗隻排便次數較頻密，腸胃亦較健康。<br />\n<br />\n排泄物關注組織指出，狗隻是四足動物，上樓梯時所造成的腸道蠕動會增強，有利排便。研究人員抽查50座附近有大型屋苑的行人天橋，收集其排泄物，並與附近路面所收集得的排泄物進行比較。研究人員把所有排泄物交由電腦分析，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有65%的排泄物含有狗隻DNA，其餘的則是人類排泄物</span></strong>。研究發現行人天橋上狗隻排泄物比路面狗隻排泄物的重量重75-96%，而且行人天橋的樓梯愈多，天橋上的狗隻排泄物就愈多。而排泄物質量方面，行人天橋上的狗隻排泄物多呈長條狀，路面的則多呈泥狀及粒狀，而且前者普遍較後者甘甜。研究結果證實了狗隻的上樓梯後有利排泄，且排泄物會有更理想的外觀及味道。組織呼籲狗主應在家設置小型樓梯，好讓狗隻可以在家排泄。<br />\n<br />\n不過，另有研究指出狗隻的骨骼結構不適合上落樓梯，經常上落樓梯的狗隻有較大風險患上關節炎。而且若沒有妥善處理排泄物或會遭受撿控，因此狗主帶狗隻上行人天橋排便前必須三思。</blockquote>"}]}